---

<section class="card about-card">
  <span class="eyebrow">About me</span>
  <div class="about-grid">

    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="about-lead">
        Good content isn't just written — it's managed, optimized, and built to be found.
      </p>
      <p>
        At Akamai, I work with AEM, analytics tools, and AI agents to make content not just
        publishable — but discoverable, localized, and easier to manage at scale.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work, I travel with a camera. My favourites live in the
        <a href="/photos">Photo Book</a> — Rajasthan, Vietnam, and the Bramhatal trek.
      </p>
      <div class="about-links">
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/adityar-singh/" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 0 1-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 1 1 2.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
          </svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/adityarsingh" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/>
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-photo-col">
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/photos/bramhatal/IMG_0439-scaled.jpg" alt="Bramhatal Trek — Garhwal Himalayas" />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about-card {
  padding: var(--card-py) var(--card-px);
}

.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 260px;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: start;
}

.about-text {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
}

.about-lead {
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  line-height: 1.55;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}

.about-text p {
  font-size: 14.5px;
  line-height: 1.78;
  color: var(--color-body-text);
}

.about-text a {
  color: var(--color-ink);
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
}

.about-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 18px;
  margin-top: 8px;
  align-items: center;
}

.social-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--color-body-text);
  text-decoration: none;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  transition: color 0.1s;
}
.social-link:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

.about-photo-col { flex-shrink: 0; }

.about-photo {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--color-hairline);
}
.about-photo img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
  display: block;
}

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .about-grid  { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .about-photo { aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; }
}

@media (max-width: 540px) {
  .about-card { padding: 28px 24px; }
}
</style>
